snippet.title: Announcing The Walking Dead: The Telltale Definitive Series!
snippet.description:
You've never seen Clementine's journey like this before.

Be part of the ultimate #StillNotBitten experience with The Walking Dead: The Telltale Definitive Series. Over 50 hours of content across 23 distinct episodes with brand-new enhancements, updates, and improvements make this the optimal #TWDG adventure for old fans AND new! 

Preorder our amazing Collector's Packs to get access to the unsurpassed digital compendium and our EXCLUSIVE collectibles available only in these definitive editions.

For full details and to preorder now, click here: http://bit.ly/TWD_DefSeries
